  Francesco Avigliano

  Independent Research Laboratory
  Contribution and Research Protocol - Private Use


  This project is an autonomous personal research laboratory. To maintain the architectural integrity and algorithmic rigor of the research, external contributions (Pull Requests) or proposals are not
  accepted.

  PROJECT NATURE:


  All identified technical challenges are resolved internally by the laboratory based on real-world operational needs and a specific proprietary research roadmap.

  FEEDBACK AND BUG REPORTING:


  While the project is closed to direct contribution, the "Issues" section may be used exclusively for reporting critical bugs or technical malfunctions in the current implementation.


  Before opening an issue, please ensure that:
  ◦ The bug is reproducible.
  ◦ You provide a detailed description of the system state.
  ◦ The issue is purely technical and not a request for new features.

  Thank you for respecting the independent nature of this research.

